data.description: Welcome to your dream Florida home! Located in the beautiful, gated 55+ community of Twin Lake, this stunning Cocoa Floor Plan Elevation B is a must see. This home offers 3 Bedroom, 2.5-bathroom with a pocket office. Step inside and you will be wowed by the 10-foot ceilings, crown molding, tray ceilings and lovely luxury vinyl wood flooring that runs throughout. You'll find an oversized island in the kitchen with granite counter tops, upgraded 42" wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances with microwave oven combo. Enjoy filtered drinking water from the kitchen’s osmosis water system. Stainless steel hood vent that adds so much character to one area. Walk in pantry with shelving. Ceiling fans and custom lighting, The master bathroom has dual sinks and plenty of counter space with an oversized shower featuring two shower heads and bench for ultimate relaxation. Bluetooth speaker hookup perfect for jamming while you are getting ready. You'll also enjoy 4 sliding glass doors that open to one side leading out to your private screened back porch with beautiful brick pavers. 2 car garage with epoxy flooring and extra storage racks. A large laundry room with plenty of folding space and cabinet space perfect for stocking up on your household cleaning supplies. Home is wired for cameras and easy to install.  Centrally located near Disney World, 417 highway, beaches, and local shopping/dining spots - Twin Lake Community offers lakefront resort-style pool plus multiple heated pools, boating and kayaking, fitness center, tennis courts & pickleball courts for those looking for recreational activities or just want to socialize. There's even a poker room available! Don’t miss out on this one-of-a-kind opportunity - make this incredible house your home today!
